🧠 Scenario 1: Temperature Cleaning & Labeling

You have a dataset weather with a column temp_c.

Tasks:

Replace missing temperatures with the average temperature.
Create a category:
"cold" if < 10
"moderate" if 10–25
"hot" if > 25
Keep only the used columns.
🧠 Scenario 2: Salary Adjustment

Dataset: employees with column salary.

Tasks:

Write a function to increase salary:
If salary < 3000 → +20%
Otherwise → +10%
Create a category:
"low" < 3000
"mid" 3000–7000
"high" > 7000
Use mutate() to apply both.
